description:
Ira Madison III (host of the Keep It! podcast) joins Danny to break down this week's Vanderpump Rules, which features (some of) the cast heading to Mexico, and the official opening of TomTom. They also briefly touch on the state of the Housewives (#RHOA & #RHOBH).


Ira Madison: 3:27ish
